Empty app. No todos, so the app omits the main section and the footer. With the
main section gone the mark-all toggle is hidden, so the header projects as the
input alone with an empty value.
Pins: toggle-hidden form `> "value"`; no item lines; no footer line.

-- dom.html --
<section class="todoapp">
	<header class="header">
		<h1>todos</h1>
		<input class="new-todo" placeholder="What needs to be done?">
	</header>
</section>

-- projection.txt --
> ""
